title: Belgium claim Euro 2016 spot by beating Andorra 4-1
text: • Italy beat Azerbaijan 2-1 in Baku to be certain of a top-two finish in Group H • Belgium routed Andorra 4-1 to overtake Wales in Group B *Italy *and... guardian.co.uk 6 hours ago - UK Belgium cruised to a 4-1 away victory over Andorra on Saturday, sealing their qualification for Euro 2016.
